Aanlysis of big contracts in Tehrans Municipality

Introduction

This document provides some insights from a public dataset provided by Tehrans Municipality. The dataset is about the big contracts of Tehrans Municipality from 2010 to present. You may find the the data here.For any reason that you couldnt retrieve the streaming data, you my find the data in the data folder of this repository. The final report is not in English language so it will not provided here. For data cleaning, I had to use some REGEX in Persian(Farsi) language.
